{{main|英雄聯盟賽事列表}}
《英雄聯盟》在電子競技領域裡獲得巨大的成功，世界各地每年都會舉辦全球总决赛和其它大小賽事<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/12/technology/riot-games-league-of-legends-main-attraction-esports.html|publisher=''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]''|title=Behind League of Legends, E-Sports's Main Attraction|last=Segal|first=David|date=2014-10-10|accessdate=2017-02-03|archive-date=2015-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907210326/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/12/technology/riot-games-league-of-legends-main-attraction-esports.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在電子競技方面，截至2016年6月為止，《英雄聯盟》共有4083名職業玩家、舉辦了1718場大小賽事，相形之下、《Dota 2》的職業玩家是1495名，舉辦的賽事有613場。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://techvibes.com/2016/06/21/how-videogames-became-a-sport-and-why-theyre-here-to-stay-hint-money|title=How Videogames Became a Sport, and Why They're Here to Stay (Hint: Money!)|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-03|archive-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710183703/https://techvibes.com/2016/06/21/how-videogames-became-a-sport-and-why-theyre-here-to-stay-hint-money|dead-url=no}}</ref>

